},\n    \"sampleD.bismark.cov\": {\n      \"_file\": \"sampleD.bismark.cov\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"meta.json\": {\n    \"_file\": \"meta.json\"\n  },\n  \"output\": {}\n}\n```\n\nSuccess hint: when `output/unite_stats.tsv` exists under the workspace, you may call submit_done(success=true).\n"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_2hNHTvqFKetXdxSi93sEGLGu", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"plan\": \"1. Load the four per-sample bismark-style coverage files using `methylKit::methRead` with the specified parameters.\\n2. Use `methylKit::unite` to unite the methylation data.\\n3. Save the united methylBase object to `output/mk_united.rds` using `saveRDS`.\\n4. Create a single-row table with the specified columns and save it to `output/unite_stats.tsv` using `write_tsv`.\\n5. Verify the existence of `output/unite_stats.tsv` and call `submit_done(success=true)` if it exists.\"}", "name": "write_plan"}}]}, {"role": "tool", "content": "Wrote plan (470 chars) to .plan.md", "name": "write_plan", "tool_call_id": "call_2hNHTvqFKetXdxSi93sEGLGu"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_sWxwfzK9fFwpxhbTTN4rMmki", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"code\": \"library(methylKit)\\n\\n# Define file paths\\nfile.list <- list(\\n  \\\"input/sampleA.bismark.cov\\\",\\n  \\\"input/sampleB.bismark.cov\\\",\\n  \\\"input/sampleC.bismark.cov\\\",\\n  \\\"input/sampleD.bismark.cov\\\"\\n)\\n\\n# Load methylation data\\nmk_raw <- methRead(\\n  file.list,\\n  pipeline = \\\"bismarkCoverage\\\",\\n  mincov = 4,\\n  treatment = c(0, 0, 1, 1),\\n  assembly = \\\"mock_v1\\\"\\n)\\n\\n# Unite methylation data\\nmk_united <- unite(mk_raw, min.per.group = 1, destrand = FALSE)\\n\\n# Save united methylBase object\\nsaveRDS(mk_united, \\\"output/mk_united.rds\\\")\\n\\n# Create unite stats\\nunite_stats <- data.frame(\\n  n_samples = length(mk_united@sample.ids),\\n  n_sit